  headline="Insurance for Offshore and Maritime Workers"
  subheadline="Your workplace is miles from shore—on an oil platform in the North Sea, a container ship crossing the Pacific, or a wind farm in the North Atlantic. When medical emergencies happen at sea, ordinary insurance assumptions don't apply. Here's how maritime workers can ensure they're properly covered."
  canonicalPath="/guides/offshore-maritime-insurance"
